title: Sketchbook Folio, "Ocean Inlet with Rocks and Two Sailboats", 1870–85
medium: Graphite on cream wove paper, bound
provenance: Anna Richards Brewster, Scarsdale, NY, 1905-1952; William T. Brewster
creditline: Gift of the National Academy of Design from the Mrs. William T. Brewster Bequest
description: Beach with large, rocky land mass at left and calm water at right. Across water, an outcropping of land. On horizon, at center, two small boats in far distance.
